    <section>
        <title>Overview</title>
        <para>SIP Service Broker is a JSLEE Resource Adaptor that offers session orchestration.
        It puts independent SIP services in the chain which allow to trigger different features within a single
        call session.
        </para>
        <para>Currently the broker can orchestrate services that are deployed on external application servers.
            In the next version it will be possible to deploy services on the same JSLEE instance which will reduce
            latency and simplify configuration.
        </para>
